Dallas thermo sensor DS1820 over UART

Example is based of: 
https://github.com/dword1511/onewire-over-uart
https://www.maximintegrated.com/en/design/technical-documents/tutorials/2/214.html

Level interface:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dword1511/onewire-over-uart/master/docs/pp2od_tt.png

Board: Olimex NB IoT
Sensor use Arduino.Serial1 and board pins: TxD-P29 and RxD-P28
sensor pull-up must be ~1mA ( 3.3v - 3.3k )

serial port can be changed of dallas.h

OLED: any I2C SSD1306

Screenshot:
https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZh7iu9WAAUjG9j?format=jpg&name=large

Notes: 
The example is not optimized... just example
Do not seartch devices ID - too long time and the dog growls...
